snippet.title: [DOAXVV] New Venus Release! Introducing Reika
snippet.description:
○Official Site：https://game.doaxvv.com/en/lp.html
A new Venus "Reika" (CV: Reina Kondo) has arrived in "DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation!"
Reika is a stoic girl with an "aloof attitude" who fell into a slump while dedicating herself to competitive swimming, and visited the Venus Islands during this rough patch.
Enjoy a new vacation with Reika, the new Venus who is so "adorably troublesome" that the Boss can't help but want to support her.


○Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/doaxvvstaff/
Game Information
○Title：DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation
○Platform：Windows PC (Steam,Johren) 
○Genre：Sports Vacation
○Release Date：Steam 10 April 2019 (Wednesday), Johren 1 July 2021 (Thursday)
○In-game purchases：Free to play/In-game purchases in Steam,Johren
○hashtag：#DOAXVV
